10640820@unknown@formal@none@1@S@The plugin currently works with Microsoft Office 2003, Microsoft Office XP and Microsoft Office 2000.@1@15@@oe@30-11-2008
10640830@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Support for Microsoft Office 2007 is only available in combination with Microsoft Office 2007 SP1.@1@15@@oe@30-11-2008
10640840@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Several software companies (including Microsoft and Novell) are working on an add-in for Microsoft Office that allows reading and writing ODF files.@1@22@@oe@30-11-2008
10640850@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Currently it works only for Microsoft Word 2007 / XP / 2003.@1@12@@oe@30-11-2008
